# ğŸ¥ Emergency Room Visits Dashboard

This project provides an interactive Emergency Room (ER) Visits Dashboard designed to analyze patient flow,
wait times, satisfaction scores, and department-level performance using Power BI.

The dashboard helps healthcare administrators identify peak hours, busiest days, patient demographics,
and operational bottlenecks to improve service efficiency and patient experience.
